Project Title:
FitHub CRM – Fitness Center Management

Introduction:
FitHub CRM is a Salesforce-based application designed to manage the operations of a fitness center. The system helps automate membership management, class scheduling, trainer assignments, and booking processes.

Technology Used:

Salesforce Lightning Platform
Custom Objects
Flows
Formula Fields
Validation Rules
Reports and Dashboards

Objects Used in the System:

Member
Trainer
Class
Booking

Key Features:

Member registration and membership tracking
Trainer management and specialization tracking
Class scheduling and capacity management
Booking and payment tracking
Automated validations and formulas
Revenue and booking analytics through reports and dashboards

Conclusion:
The FitHub CRM system successfully automates fitness center operations using Salesforce. It improves efficiency, reduces manual work, and provides valuable insights through reports and dashboards.
